    "body": "```\r\nIn [1]: df = pd.DataFrame(1, index=range(3), columns=[1, 3, 2])\r\n\r\nIn [2]: df.stack()\r\nOut[2]: \r\n0  1    1\r\n   3    1\r\n   2    1\r\n1  1    1\r\n   3    1\r\n   2    1\r\n2  1    1\r\n   3    1\r\n   2    1\r\ndtype: int64\r\n\r\nIn [3]: df.stack().index.is_lexsorted()\r\nOut[3]: True\r\n\r\nIn [5]: df.stack().index.is_monotonic\r\nOut[5]: False\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe docs should read lex-sorted. Not 'sorted'."
